01:24:47.323 --> 01:24:49.118
when everyone has a knife.

01:24:50.119 --> 01:24:52.501
A knife to stop the man

01:24:53.157 --> 01:24:55.366
who can't just stop himself.

01:25:03.857 --> 01:25:05.479
