01:25:08.482 --> 01:25:09.345
Come with me.

01:25:11.278 --> 01:25:13.108
You and me. Come on.

01:25:23.704 --> 01:25:24.567
I...

01:25:27.915 --> 01:25:31.816
I just wanted us to get rescued.

01:25:50.766 --> 01:25:52.319
What are they gonna do?

